NOTE: Only shortlisted candidates will receive invitation letter with venue details to undergo selection process with unique ID and details of mandatory documents required.

 

Desired Candidate Profile:

Referred candidates MUST meet ALL of the following criteria:

  • Should have graduated in 2018
  • Should have 60% and above in 10th, 12th and 50% and above in graduation (aggregate of 8 semesters)
  • Must be from below mentioned specialization only - Information Technology, Information Science, Computer Science, Computer, Electronics, Electronics & Communication, Electronics & Telecommunication, Electrical & Electronics, Electrical, Electronics & Instrumentation, Instrumentation
  • Only 1 year gap is allowed post HSC(12th) and not after SSC(10th) or between graduation years
  • Must possess excellent English written/spoken communication skills
  • Selected candidates should be available to join immediately, if needed
  • Selected candidates will have to sign a 2-year Service Agreement on the day of joining
  • Must be open to relocate to any Capgemini location, work across technology, domain, role and should be ready to work in shifts if required.

How to Refer:

  • Please send relevant resumes to refer-freshers.in@capgemini.com with the following details

Candidate Name

  • Mention the, “Candidate Name – Preferred Interview Location” e.g. (Amit Kumar – Mumbai), in the subject line.

As per Referral Policy, referral incentives are not applicable for fresher positions. Resumes will be screened and ONLY shortlisted candidates will be issued call letter for aptitude test.
